On Mon, 3 Sep 2012, Alexandros Attikis wrote:

> Hi Sami,
> I have found some time to get to run this code.
> I would like to add to the tree branches of all 5 higgs bosons, not just Hpm.
> Could you point me to the way of doing this?
> Also, are SUSY decays saved to the tree?
Hi,
You can add more branches in file (Top2HPlus/src/)mainFH.cpp. No SUSY 
decays are included. Anything FH produces in the output can be added. Here 
is an example:
  BR_Hp_enu = sfinder.getValue("FH",*file,"Hp-nu_e-e");
Here the string "Hp-nu_e-e" is the same string as in the FH output.

